{
  "stem": "26140.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was an SS man standing in front who looks like a doctor to me, who started pointing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were two rows of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was to separate some of them, which was in the minority, which were mainly men, and women with children, and pregnant women or children themselves, there used to be put on a separate row.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later on, they were moved by the SS people to-- I knew the direction, where it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The SS men were very, very kind and good, because they were frightened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If there's about 400 people, and somebody is trying to stir them, this might be quite a commotion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometimes the transport consists of 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were so frightened that they never moved a finger at the people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were rather trying to be gentlemen and helpful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A woman with a child, he tried to hold it for her and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I knew this was only in order to avoid any panic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But sometimes, you could see a chap that he was saying, where are you taking us?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are you going to gas us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, they knew he is there to annoy all the others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they just took him out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Took him so far away, nobody's seen it, and shot him so there was no more-- any disturbance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as far as I know, they went to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were told that they going to be having a wash, delouse, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Put your things down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were moved into another room, which they called a washroom, which didn't look like a washroom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they made it look like.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put tops and everything, so that people would think it's a washroom.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
